+# Vegas Blitz Deterministic Core Oracle Cases
+
+Notation:
+- Windows are 6 reels x 4 rows.
+- Payout expectations are in paytable units unless `xBet` or `total bet` is stated.
+- `COR(10x)` means a Coin symbol carrying a 10x total-bet value.
+- These cases are simulator-core cases only; UI, buttons, sounds, logs, popups, and server forcing are out of scope.
+
+## TC-BASE-001 No Win Base Window
+
+MODE: BASE
+BET_FIXED_COINS: 20
+
+FULL_WINDOW:
+row 0 | HV1 | HV2 | HV3 | HV4 | HV5 | LV1
+row 1 | LV2 | LV3 | LV4 | LV5 | LV6 | HV1
+row 2 | HV2 | HV3 | HV4 | HV5 | LV1 | LV2
+row 3 | LV3 | LV4 | LV5 | LV6 | HV1 | HV2
+
+EXPECT:
+- ways_win = 0
+- scatter_win = 0
+- collect_win = 0
+- feature_trigger = none
+
+## TC-BASE-002 Standard 2OAK Ways Win
+
+MODE: BASE
+BET_FIXED_COINS: 20
+
+FULL_WINDOW:
+row 0 | HV1 | HV1 | LV1 | LV2 | LV3 | LV4
+row 1 | LV2 | LV3 | LV4 | LV5 | LV6 | HV2
+row 2 | HV3 | HV4 | HV5 | LV1 | LV2 | LV3
+row 3 | LV4 | LV5 | LV6 | HV2 | HV3 | HV4
+
+EXPECT:
+- HV1 count by consecutive reels = 1 x 1, stops on reel 3
+- HV1 kind = 2OAK
+- HV1 paytable = 20
+- ways_win = 20
+- scatter_win = 0
+- collect_win = 0
+- feature_trigger = none
+
+## TC-BASE-003 WILD Substitution Ways Win
+
